Version history of slot-machine and changes

Version 1.0.0 - The basic idea slot machine was created, you could spin for money, and well that was it. You had infinite money.

Version 1.0.7 - First version that was made public, introduced the bank, and loan system. UI updates and more.

Version 1.0.7.1 - Bug fixes and grammar fixes

Version 1.0.8 - Huge UI updates, everthing is now more streamlined and readible. Fixed a bug where you could not pay loans back
